labels.label:
This flow is used to load Dunkin store software data (CSV) to DB Algorithm is given below -
1. Read CSV from S3 bucket. 2. Backup that file. 3. Take required columns. 4. Required Validation. 5. Data Transformation & Insertion into persistent store. 5.1 Update duplicate data.
